{"tid":1262802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】政圈流傳林鄭提請辭 特首辦：無此事！","createTime":"2019-06-28T01:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T01:02:24.000Z","uid":143078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6c3c98ace5c9021d3bfb69de295a2d43fd20d84c","tid":1262802,"uid":143078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:01:23.000Z","msg":"張圖邊度見過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEFOa2J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEFOa2J.jpg&h=d26acf14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政圈傳出林鄭月娥已向中央政府提出請辭，《蘋果》向特首辦查詢，發言人回覆時直指「無此事」，至於特首未來兩周有何公眾活動？發言人稱就行政長官的公開活動，可留意相關採訪通知；至於行會會否再休會，發言人則指若行會安排有更改，政府會有公佈。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190627/59764611\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F59764611&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=0ed4e4b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F59764611&h=00615194\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190627/59764611</a>"},{"pid":"a27d26e3a79543f1e7483a771f5f1209bce759cd","tid":1262802,"uid":3127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:02:24.000Z","msg":"燒山出少句聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}